meta {
  name: 4. Resolve — pip (Product Information Page)
  type: http
  seq: 4
}

get {
  url: {{dl-url}}/01/{{gtin}}?linkType=gs1:pip
  body: none
  auth: none
}

docs {
  Requesting the gs1:pip link type returns a 302 redirect to the product page on
  demo.epcis.cloud. Bruno follows redirects by default (you'll land on the DDM
  page, 200). To *show* the raw 302 + Location header in the demo, turn off
  "Follow Redirects" (request Settings tab, or Bruno preferences).
}
